Running into issue where upon entering any game, even when creating a new one, no buildings are clickable and no buttons do anything, including the exit to menu. I will post a screenshot of my mods and tell you that they are all up to date as far as possible.

https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B6tFtD_XfdzIQ1ItMG1SbWV6M2M/view?usp=sharing log

https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B6tFtD_XfdzIVzVrM2RRTFd4VGs/view?usp=sharing mods

I hope I've done this right, thanks for any help you can provide
Uninstall every mod that is 1.0.5 compatible and is not said to be 1.1. I am assuming that is 1.1? If it isn't run 1.0.5 32bit.
